Holding.txt File (Order Acknowledgement)
The Holding.txt file serves as your order acknowledgement for your integration purchase order. It is
produced within 15 minutes after you submit your order. The processor converts the details data
(Inventory Key and Size Index) into the holding file as style, color, and size. The holding file also displays
the ship-from warehouse and product availability flag (Y or N) which tells you if there is stock for the
submitted line item.
SanMar will check inventory prior to placing an order and will source each order from the closest
warehouse to the destination zip code. If the inventory is unavailable, a SanMar customer service
representative will notify the customer via phone for permission to ship short orfind an alternate item
to replace the out-of-stock inventory.
